Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.50,0:00:10.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂雏 你看看这屋子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.28,0:00:13.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是一直保持着原样直到你出院啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:17.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你不就打扫一下屋子 可怎么就变成了这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.57,0:00:21.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说啊 说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.24,0:00:24.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,连我刚买的壶都阵亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.90,0:00:26.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会再原谅你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.61,0:00:29.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我要和你断绝关系
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,OP
