Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.40,0:00:44.40,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}偶然一瞬 想起了你的容貌模样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.12,0:01:05.48,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}在记忆之中 你微笑着的侧脸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.75,0:01:11.16,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}平淡无奇的日常 是无可替的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.24,0:01:16.01,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}这份思念之情 现在终于意识到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.17,0:01:18.82,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}和你欢笑度过的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.82,0:01:21.63,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}和你争论泪流的曾经
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.65,0:01:25.99,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我们携手的每一天 令人无比怜爱的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.27,0:01:28.76,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}十分珍惜
