Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:07.35,hinamatsuri_guochang,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(960,0)\pos(614,1218)}断绝关系Rock n' Roll Fever
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.41,0:02:08.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你再像之前一样恐吓威胁我也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.44,0:02:10.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,反正这里都乱成一团了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:17.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 尽管保你的重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:24.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.53,0:02:25.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:37.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,以后要怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.58,0:02:42.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,反正他也给我钱了 先去吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.01,0:02:52.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没钱了 以后要怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.28,0:02:54.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,先打打游戏再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.21,0:02:57.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是雏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.14,0:03:00.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:04.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你还没有回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:05.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一言难尽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:08.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 你也搞砸了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:10.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好好道过歉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.03,0:03:13.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,歉是道了 但他没原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:15.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 这么一点不够吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.49,0:03:16.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:19.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你以后打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:20.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 所以面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:22.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:26.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想回新田那儿去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:29.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:34.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,总之你就先在我这儿住下吧 你自己快想点办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:44.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:49.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼啊 这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.31,0:04:08.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雏 快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:11.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:19.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔给你 这是今天的杂志
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:21.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.98,0:04:23.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,给你钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:24.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:26.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去捡空罐子了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:28.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:33.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雏 差不多该醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:36.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,擅自吃别人的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.05,0:04:39.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你想过以后的计划了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:42.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想了 不过不知道该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:45.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,游戏机都没电了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.33,0:04:47.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙 到底想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:49.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,芳香醇厚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.74,0:04:51.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雏不在家 白天也能品尝美酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:04:57.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说这傻丫头哭着回来求我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:00.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.08,0:05:04.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我是渡边中学的三岛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.94,0:05:06.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你是那个调酒…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.84,0:05:08.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是雏的同班同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:10.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我给她拿来了学校的作业
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:12.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.84,0:05:14.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你能放在信箱里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:19.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 雏感冒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:23.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在有点不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:25.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她回我老家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.79,0:05:27.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:29.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.42,0:05:31.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还有学校这档子事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:34.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.24,0:05:37.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是假期 为什么会回老家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.76,0:05:40.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这又是家事 不好过问啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:41.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:43.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.66,0:05:44.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诗子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.00,0:05:48.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在人手不够了 过来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:48.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,帮什么忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:54.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可以再给我一点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:58.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 还要给别人呢 平等平等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.51,0:05:59.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:00.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:02.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,给我饭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:04.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雏？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:05.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 诗子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:06.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会在这儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:07.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,给我饭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:09.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 快一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:12.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.94,0:06:16.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雏 咱们该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:17.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:21.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是小瞳吧 真是帮了大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:22.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:24.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.09,0:06:24.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.14,0:06:27.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道小雏最近出什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:31.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,断绝关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:33.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.32,0:06:34.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么狠心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:37.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是没看到那个惨相
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:41.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底 你知道那家伙费了我多少钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:43.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是一点好处都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:47.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.32,0:06:50.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,养孩子怎么能说什么好处不好处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:53.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是看她孤身一人才收留她的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:57.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我确实是这么说过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:07:01.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不是这小屁孩的老爸 不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.01,0:07:09.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能跟他们说雏是突然从天上掉下来的就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:12.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊 我一直没插嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:13.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你这口气算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:15.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你还算是个父亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:16.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:19.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不论如何这样还是太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:21.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是无话可说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:32.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 你们究竟是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.29,0:07:38.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,滚出去……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:51.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳 去拿盐过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:55.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:56.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.42,0:07:58.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你得把新田的酒钱付了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:05.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不管她现在过得怎么样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.89,0:08:10.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,连杏子都努力活下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.23,0:08:12.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她肯定行的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:20.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我还特意坐了单人沙发
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:23.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,落了个坏习惯啊 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:29.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:31.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,蜡烛可不是免费的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.10,0:08:34.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我再看一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:37.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那本杂志本来是能卖钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:38.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我很闲嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:41.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,薯片吃完了 没了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:43.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:46.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,随便吃我的东西 懒懒散散就会在这睡懒觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.30,0:08:49.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本就没考虑过要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.56,0:08:54.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不照顾你了 我要和你绝交
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:02.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,以后该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:06.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟新田在一起的时候真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:11.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但我怎么才能回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:18.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他最生气的就是我把壶弄碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:22.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没钱
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,——插入曲——
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:28.40,hinamatsuri_insert,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}眩しいすぎるぜ　サンライズ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:30.50,hinamatsuri_insert,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}でもまだ僕でいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.52,0:09:32.50,hinamatsuri_insert,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}遠すぎる二人のたり
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:37.94,hinamatsuri_insert,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}それはディスタンス
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,hinamatsuri_insert,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:28.40,hinamatsuri_insert,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}过于耀眼的Sunrise
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:30.50,hinamatsuri_insert,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}但是仍想保持自我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.52,0:09:32.50,hinamatsuri_insert,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}分隔得过于遥远的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:37.94,hinamatsuri_insert,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}这就是Distance
