Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:51.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚真是干得不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:54.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,淳你这歌喉还是一如既往的棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.56,0:10:00.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.98,0:10:02.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才就在这里听了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:05.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们乐队怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:08.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个先不提 我想问你们一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.06,0:10:14.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,分发食物的时候她们还在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:17.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那她应该去杏子那边住了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:20.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒并不是在意她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.17,0:10:25.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是来看看她 确认一下她是不是因为我死翘翘了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:26.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:27.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是杏子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:29.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么在这里鬼鬼祟祟的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.74,0:10:31.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没 没什么 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:32.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,散步啦 散步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:36.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,散步就在公园门口转来转去吗 是不是脑子出问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:40.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不说这个了 先说说雏的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.81,0:10:42.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,连你也要责怪我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.06,0:10:43.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.88,0:10:49.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前真能把她照顾好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:52.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我三天就跟她绝交了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:53.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.94,0:10:55.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:01.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙 连流浪汉都不如
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.88,0:11:06.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子 就算你现在展示你的活法也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:14.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没耍小聪明 也没有机关
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.87,0:11:24.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雏 你这魔术好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:28.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们虽然原来在这儿是最卖座的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:29.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但最近被你给打败了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:32.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等下咱们去吃个饭庆祝一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:33.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.53,0:11:35.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:38.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥 我找到小雏了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:42.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧来找我哭一哭 认个错就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:45.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雏这家伙弄得我这么不安
